imdb.plot outline: The Massachusetts-based cable television show stars Harrison Young. The native New Englander usually conducts hour-long interviews with a variety of talented individuals who work in businesses that specialize in advertising, art, comedy, dining, fashion, health, lifestyles, literature, marketing, movies, music, promotions, publishing, radio, sports, television, and live theatre. The interviews are conducted either in-studio or on location.
